Installation Steps for SASS:

1. Created directory structure:
   - Navigated to alx-intermediate-frontend repository
   - Created 0x03-sass_scss directory
   - Navigated into the new directory

2. Installed Node.js (if using Linux installation):
   - Ran: curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
   - Exited and reopened terminal
   - Installed Node.js version 20.16

3. Installed SASS:
   - Ran: npm install sass -v 3.7.4

4. Verified installation by checking SASS version
